parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to jerk, vibrate, or accelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or shudders when shifting gears

especially when stopping or accelerating; the transmission shifts roughly or hesitates; the vehicle vibrates or shudders at certain RPM ranges; the vehicle accelerates or decelerates unexpectedly; the transmission holds a gear for an extended period.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unpredictable transmission behavior can cause the vehicle to accelerate or decelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates or decelerates suddenly without warning; the transmission shifts erratically; the vehicle hesitates or stalls when accelerating; the vehicle lurches forward or backward unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to inconvenience, safety risks, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage or disengage properly; the vehicle is unable to shift gears; the transmission slips or hesitates; the vehicle is unable to move.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause safety features like hands-free options to malfunction, and can also lead to inconvenience and frustration for the driver.
symptoms: Cracked or unresponsive CUE screen
spiderweb effect on the radio screen
inability to see or use features like Bluetooth
navigation
and AC fan speed control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The issue with the fuel tank can cause inconvenience and frustration for the driver, leading to longer filling times.
symptoms: The gas fuel tank continuously stops while pumping gas
making it take longer to fill up the tank.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a fire hazard, leading to a potential safety risk for the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Radio and heated seats acting erratically
radio turning up and down by itself
heated seats turning on and off
electrical burning smell
smoke and flames coming from under the passenger seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to occupants.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries or fatalities to occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause unexpected and potentially hazardous situations, distracting the driver and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unnecessarily
such as when hitting a curb
without any physical damage to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag indicator can cause concern and uncertainty for the driver, potentially leading to distraction and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The airbag indicator illuminates without any apparent reason
such as when placing a mobile phone on the passenger seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power steering can cause the vehicle to become difficult to control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power steering
difficulty turning the steering wheel
overcompensation of the steering wheel
violent turns
spinning out of control.
